		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「庇护」标记玩家，在原地进行吟唱，并在标记处产生爆炸，爆炸和冲击波都造成<span color="#99ff85">90%,22.5%</span><span>伤害，同时产生2枚较小的图纹，爆裂造成</span><span color="#99ff85">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1412" y="223" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「庇护」召唤7枚图纹，呈三叉样分布，图纹迸裂造成<span color="#99ff85">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「庇护」朝玩家方向蓄力，迸发草元素脉冲，造成<span color="#99ff85">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「庇护」将玩家带入「<span textDecoration="underline">抉择之域</span><span>」，自己则暂时退入「夜魂灵隙」。领域内不断生成夜魂战士，在其周围有一圈毒雾，靠近将持续造成基于敌方</span><span color="#99ff85">30%</span><span>攻击力的伤害。需与「夜魂灵隙」交互后方可退出领域。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_13.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
