		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#389a3e" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#389a3e">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="61" y="373" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="434" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" color="#ffffff">依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffb3" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_17.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_18.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_19.png')" x="596" y="459" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_20.png')" x="576" y="438" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="438" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每击败「抉择之域」中的一名夜魂战士，全队都会获得「咒祝」：获得<span color="#ffccbf">60%</span><span>的增伤，但以此为代价的是当前角色会每</span><span color="#ff9999">0.5秒</span><span>流失</span><span color="#ffccbf">(1%+50)</span><span>生命值，以上效果均可叠加。流血效果在退出「抉择之域」后移除，而增伤效果持续15s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/依奇卡胡伊皮利的庇护.assets/Image_21.png')" x="720" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="912" width="432" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">抉择之域：「庇护」将玩家带入的特殊领域，此领域内会持续刷新夜魂战士敌人(疾迅勇士系列)，击败以获得提升效果，可随时与夜魂灵隙交互退出。<br/>低于<span color="#ffcebf">80%</span><span>生命值后，「庇护」将强制展开一次领域。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
